--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.1.4 (2020-12-18)
E: Revert to process PID file in Monit check

* Version 0.1.3 (2020-12-18)
B: Use process name pattern matching in Monit check

* Version 0.1.2 (2020-12-15)
E: Add install_recommends parameter to package tasks

* Version 0.1.1 (2020-12-12)
B: Run 'apt update' after adding Grafana repository
B: Correct grafana.gpg file path

* Version 0.1.0 (2020-12-12)
F: Initial release
